Interface ImmutableBag<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E -
    All Superinterfaces:
    Iterable<E>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Bag

    public interface ImmutableBag<E>
extends Iterable<E>
    A non-modifiable bag.

    A bag is a set that can also hold duplicates. Also known as multiset.

    Author:
    Arni Arent
